videos.description: Houston's Kyle Meyer throws down a put-back dunk off Rob Gray's miss.
videos.headline: Houston's Kyle Meyer starts off the game with put-back slam

videos.description: Houston's Galen Robinson Jr. makes the athletic lay-in  to tie the game at 51.
videos.headline: Galen Robinson goes coast-to-coast for the and-1 layup

videos.description: SMU's Sterling Brown gets fouled on a made layup to put SMU ahead 60-53 over Houston.
videos.headline: SMU makes and-1 layup to expand lead over Houston
